WEBVTT

00:01.543 --> 00:02.585
[ mouse squeaks ]

00:03.128 --> 00:04.128
[ penguins wenk ]

00:06.673 --> 00:07.673
[ all cheering ]

00:10.552 --> 00:11.552
[ screeches ]

00:13.430 --> 00:14.514
♪ Adventure Time ♪

00:14.598 --> 00:15.765
♪ Come on,
grab your friends ♪

00:15.849 --> 00:18.476
♪ We'll go to very
distant lands ♪

00:18.560 --> 00:19.519
♪ With Jake the dog ♪

00:19.603 --> 00:20.770
♪ And Finn the human ♪

00:20.854 --> 00:22.396
♪ The fun will never end ♪

00:22.481 --> 00:24.357
♪ lt's Adventure Time ♪

00:32.824 --> 00:33.824
[ birds chirping ]

00:33.909 --> 00:35.034
FINN:
[ laughs ]

00:35.118 --> 00:36.619
Awwww...
Yes!

00:36.703 --> 00:37.537
[ chuckles ]

00:37.621 --> 00:38.704
[ deep voice ]
Oh, yeah.

00:38.789 --> 00:39.622
[ laughs ]

00:39.706 --> 00:41.791
Jake, get ready for
a slap in the jowls!

00:41.875 --> 00:42.708
[ laughs ]

00:42.793 --> 00:44.544
Seriously, though,
get ready...

00:44.628 --> 00:45.920
[ continues laughing ]

00:46.004 --> 00:47.922
...for a day filled
with adventure!

00:48.006 --> 00:49.006
Whoa, really?!

00:49.091 --> 00:49.882
Yeah, man!

00:49.967 --> 00:51.467
[ laughs and snorts ]

00:51.552 --> 00:54.387
l wrote on my arm this
"To Do" list of cool junk.

00:54.471 --> 00:56.514
Number one --
Backflip off this

00:56.598 --> 00:58.391
bridge and do the splits.

00:58.475 --> 01:00.851
Number two --
Track down and slay

01:00.936 --> 01:02.687
a Goblin Horde.

01:02.771 --> 01:04.605
Number three --
Storm clouds?

01:04.690 --> 01:05.606
Hmm.

01:05.691 --> 01:06.607
[ gasps ]

01:06.692 --> 01:08.442
Finn, it's a knife storm!

01:08.527 --> 01:09.443
[ laughs and snorts ]

01:09.528 --> 01:10.528
lt's rainin' knives, man!

01:10.612 --> 01:11.571
Come on!

01:11.655 --> 01:14.365
l've never seen a
knife storm before.

01:14.449 --> 01:15.283
lt's beautiful!

01:17.327 --> 01:19.453
Looks like we're staying
in today, kid.

01:19.538 --> 01:21.247
Well, what are we gonna do?

01:21.331 --> 01:24.584
Who wants to
play video games?

01:24.668 --> 01:25.626
BOTH:
Beemo!

01:25.711 --> 01:28.045
What's on the menu, Beemo?

01:28.130 --> 01:31.299
l've created a new game
called "Conversation Parade."

01:31.383 --> 01:32.592
Start it up, Beemo.

01:32.676 --> 01:33.801
All right!

01:33.885 --> 01:38.723
♪ What do you think about
the stars in the sky? ♪

01:38.807 --> 01:39.849
lt's okay, I guess.

01:39.933 --> 01:40.933
Yeah, they're cool.

01:41.018 --> 01:44.437
♪ That is an interesting response ♪

01:44.521 --> 01:46.772
Battery low! Shut down.

01:46.857 --> 01:48.816
- Boo!
- Beemo, that was weak.

01:48.900 --> 01:49.734
What now?

01:49.818 --> 01:50.860
Hey, ooh, ooh, dude,

01:50.944 --> 01:53.070
l know something totally
rockin' we can do!

01:53.155 --> 01:54.030
Whoa! What?

01:54.114 --> 01:56.115
Let's use our of imaginations, man!

01:56.199 --> 01:57.325
Barf that!

01:57.409 --> 01:59.118
lmagination is
for turbo nerds

01:59.202 --> 02:01.746
who can't handle how
kick-butt reality is.

02:01.830 --> 02:04.999
l'm a kick-butt
reality Master!

02:05.083 --> 02:08.169
l would rather die
than be imaginative.

02:08.252 --> 02:09.419
l mean that.

02:09.503 --> 02:11.881
Eh, your loss.

02:11.965 --> 02:14.800
Aah! Lava!
Lava all around us!

02:14.885 --> 02:15.718
[ shouting ]

02:17.846 --> 02:19.347
Lava on the floor!

02:19.431 --> 02:20.389
Shut up, man.

02:20.474 --> 02:21.766
Seriously, man, there

02:21.850 --> 02:24.018
must be an enchantment
on the house or something!

02:24.102 --> 02:27.229
l'm not playing your
child-style games, guy.

02:27.314 --> 02:29.982
Watch and learn
as l master...

02:30.067 --> 02:30.900
Reality.

02:33.445 --> 02:35.363
Noooooo!

02:35.447 --> 02:37.365
[ sizzling ]

02:37.449 --> 02:39.325
Aaaaaaaaah!

02:39.409 --> 02:40.618
[ shouting ]

02:40.702 --> 02:41.869
Jake, what the hay-hay?!

02:41.953 --> 02:43.287
l was just playing around
with my imagination,

02:43.372 --> 02:44.664
and then everything got intense.

02:47.542 --> 02:48.793
lt's like...

02:48.877 --> 02:50.294
Whatever you imagine
becomes real.

02:50.379 --> 02:51.379
That's bananas!

02:51.463 --> 02:53.798
Don't imagine blowing
apart my own brain!

02:53.882 --> 02:55.299
Don't imagine my
eyeballs coming

02:55.384 --> 02:57.385
alive and flying around
with rocket packs!

02:57.469 --> 02:58.678
Dude, imagine that

02:58.762 --> 03:00.054
Beemo invented
a better video

03:00.138 --> 03:01.931
game and that he
has new batteries.

03:02.015 --> 03:02.848
BOTH:
Whoa!

03:02.933 --> 03:05.101
But first,
stop imagining lava!

03:05.185 --> 03:06.644
[ grunts ]
l can't!

03:06.728 --> 03:08.229
My imagination's
too amazing!

03:08.313 --> 03:10.690
lmagine turning
your imagination off.

03:10.774 --> 03:11.982
l can't, dude.

03:12.067 --> 03:18.531
But l think l can imagine an
imagination-turning-off machine

03:18.615 --> 03:22.535
that is upstairs, surrounded by
a crudload of traps, ghosts,

03:22.619 --> 03:24.620
monsters, and poison fountains

03:24.705 --> 03:27.665
and -- and girls!

03:27.749 --> 03:28.833
Cute girls and hamsters!

03:28.917 --> 03:31.544
Can't you make it easier
to get to that machine?

03:31.628 --> 03:33.754
You can't hold
this baby back.

03:33.839 --> 03:35.548
That's bad parenting, Mama!

03:35.632 --> 03:40.928
Then it's up to me to take
your imagination Downtown!

03:41.012 --> 03:43.222
Let's go to the den
and suit up!

03:43.306 --> 03:44.306
JAKE:
Neat!

03:44.391 --> 03:45.224
Grab that missile.

03:45.308 --> 03:46.100
Okay.

03:46.184 --> 03:47.810
And get that
Cosmic Gauntlet.

03:47.894 --> 03:48.811
Nah.

03:48.895 --> 03:50.771
There's a better one
over by the desk.

03:50.856 --> 03:52.398
[ grunts ]
Unh!

03:52.482 --> 03:53.983
Ow. What did l just hit?

03:54.067 --> 03:55.693
l'm imagining a wall.

03:55.777 --> 03:57.194
You can just go around it.

03:57.279 --> 03:58.195
Really?

03:58.280 --> 03:59.572
That's it?

03:59.656 --> 04:02.867
There isn't any invisible,
angry troll or anything?

04:02.951 --> 04:04.285
Well, there's one now.

04:04.369 --> 04:05.619
- [ troll growls ]
- Look out!

04:05.704 --> 04:08.038
Aah, l can feel
it on my foot!

04:08.123 --> 04:09.373
Whoa!

04:09.458 --> 04:10.458
[ troll grunting ]

04:10.542 --> 04:11.876
l'll kill you, Troll!

04:11.960 --> 04:13.919
Hyah! Hyah! Hyah!
Hyah! Hyah! Hyah!

04:14.004 --> 04:15.880
You're kicking
too high!

04:15.964 --> 04:17.130
He's shorter than you!

04:17.214 --> 04:19.007
[ grunting ]

04:19.091 --> 04:20.091
All right!

04:20.177 --> 04:21.385
You're getting him, man!

04:21.470 --> 04:22.553
[ grunting ]

04:22.637 --> 04:25.222
Uh-oh. Now you're
upper-cutting his family.

04:25.307 --> 04:26.140
[ woman shouts ]

04:26.224 --> 04:28.851
[ laughs ]
You just kicked his wife in the face.

04:28.935 --> 04:30.936
[ woman shouting ]

04:31.021 --> 04:32.480
She's coming back
for revenge.

04:32.564 --> 04:33.481
Cram this!

04:33.565 --> 04:35.775
We got to book it to your
imagination machine!

04:35.859 --> 04:36.901
Aah!

04:36.985 --> 04:38.903
The knife storm, remember?!

04:38.987 --> 04:39.820
[ both grunting ]

04:43.867 --> 04:45.701
[ breathing heavily ]
Whew!

04:45.786 --> 04:48.370
[ sighs, breathing heavily ]

04:48.455 --> 04:49.413
Oh, boy.

04:49.498 --> 04:51.040
Ooh!

04:51.124 --> 04:52.041
[ chuckles ]

04:52.125 --> 04:53.918
Finn, I found some candy.

04:54.002 --> 04:55.461
[ munching ]

04:55.545 --> 04:57.922
Mmm! Mm-mmm!

04:58.006 --> 05:00.508
lt tastes like banana candy, man.

05:00.592 --> 05:02.051
[ slurps ]
Mmm!

05:02.135 --> 05:03.803
Here, man. Try some.

05:03.887 --> 05:05.763
[ munches ]

05:05.847 --> 05:09.308
FINN:
Okay, try to imagine some kind of...

05:09.392 --> 05:12.937
Steel umbrella over
the bridge so...

05:13.021 --> 05:13.979
We don't get knifed.

05:14.064 --> 05:16.524
Okay.
[ grunts ]

05:16.608 --> 05:18.067
lt is done.

05:18.151 --> 05:19.360
Uh...

05:19.444 --> 05:20.236
[ laughs ]

05:20.320 --> 05:21.445
Hey, you did it, man!

05:21.530 --> 05:23.405
EVlL VOICE:
Hold, voyagers!

05:23.490 --> 05:26.325
To cross this bridge, you must

05:26.409 --> 05:29.578
first pass the test of the riddle.

05:29.663 --> 05:31.872
An imaginary Riddle Master?

05:31.957 --> 05:33.332
[ laughs ]

05:33.416 --> 05:34.333
[ sighs ]

05:34.417 --> 05:36.210
Ask me your riddle,
Riddle Master!

05:36.294 --> 05:38.379
l accept your test!

05:38.463 --> 05:42.550
Then brace yourself, fool,
for this riddle comes from a

05:42.634 --> 05:45.386
mysterious, faraway land.

05:45.470 --> 05:46.846
Lay it on me!

05:46.930 --> 05:48.806
Yes, um...

05:48.890 --> 05:51.559
The riddle --
uh, it cometh,

05:51.643 --> 05:52.434
uh...

05:52.519 --> 05:54.436
l-I can't imagine a riddle.

05:54.521 --> 05:56.438
Dude, just make it super easy.

05:56.523 --> 05:57.690
RIDDLE MASTER:
The riddle cometh!

05:57.774 --> 06:03.904
Tell me, voyager, what is
simple and yet also a riddle.

06:03.989 --> 06:05.739
Man, that riddle sucks!

06:05.824 --> 06:08.117
That is the wrong answer!

06:08.201 --> 06:10.327
The penalty is...

06:10.412 --> 06:12.496
Death by snakes!

06:12.581 --> 06:13.789
Yeah, right!

06:13.874 --> 06:15.332
l got a missile!

06:15.417 --> 06:17.585
[ shouts ]
- Nooooooooo!

06:17.669 --> 06:18.460
Aah!

06:18.545 --> 06:20.754
You exploded the
snakes right at us!

06:20.839 --> 06:22.172
l can feel them
all over my face,

06:25.886 --> 06:27.720
l'm sorry, brother!
l'm sorry!

06:27.804 --> 06:29.138
Let's just get to your
imaginary machine,

06:29.222 --> 06:31.015
and we'll be okay!

06:31.099 --> 06:33.726
Aah, a big bowl of baby
elephants, chain saws,

06:33.810 --> 06:35.811
and doo-doo is flying
towards us! Jump, dude!

06:35.896 --> 06:36.770
[ shouts ]

06:36.855 --> 06:38.731
Here comes a
soul eater!

06:38.815 --> 06:39.940
Snap its neck!

06:40.025 --> 06:41.442
Ow!
[ cackles ]

06:41.526 --> 06:42.359
[ gasps ]

06:42.444 --> 06:44.403
The Bazooka Goblin
has you in its sights!

06:44.487 --> 06:47.489
Hey, don't shoot us
with that bazooka!

06:47.574 --> 06:48.407
[ cackles ]

06:48.491 --> 06:49.783
Don't you do it!

06:49.868 --> 06:52.036
[ cackling continues ]

06:52.120 --> 06:53.829
Don't do it, man!

06:53.914 --> 06:56.040
BAZOOKA GOBLIN:
Heh heh-heh heh. Okay.

06:56.124 --> 06:57.041
Oh, yeah!

06:57.125 --> 06:57.958
[ both laugh ]

06:58.043 --> 07:00.127
All right, use your
powers or something.

07:00.211 --> 07:01.879
This poison is
about to kill me.

07:01.963 --> 07:04.548
All right. Going up!

07:04.633 --> 07:05.925
Check it --
My imagination-off

07:06.009 --> 07:07.134
machine is left of the bed.

07:07.218 --> 07:08.177
ls it clear?

07:08.261 --> 07:08.928
Yeah.

07:09.012 --> 07:10.304
l mean, there's a
bunch of cute girls,

07:10.388 --> 07:12.556
but they shouldn't
bother you.

07:12.641 --> 07:13.724
Yah!

07:13.808 --> 07:15.184
Uh, where...

07:15.268 --> 07:17.519
Where is this? l can't...

07:17.604 --> 07:18.896
Aw, man.

07:18.980 --> 07:20.648
Oh, l found the
shut-off lever!

07:20.732 --> 07:21.774
Cool, man!

07:21.858 --> 07:22.816
[ girl giggles ]

07:22.901 --> 07:24.443
Dang, girl,
if you weren't a

07:24.527 --> 07:27.154
figment of my imagination,
l'd want to have your baby.

07:27.238 --> 07:28.072
[ girl giggles ]

07:28.156 --> 07:29.198
What are you laughing at?

07:29.282 --> 07:31.200
All right,
l'm gonna turn it off.

07:31.284 --> 07:32.660
[ growls ]
- Unh!

07:32.744 --> 07:34.078
You said it was
clear of danger!

07:34.162 --> 07:36.080
Dude, l can't see anything!

07:36.164 --> 07:38.832
l must have imagined an
invisible monster!

07:38.917 --> 07:39.917
What?!

07:40.001 --> 07:41.502
Well, how do I kill it?!

07:41.586 --> 07:43.295
Ugh! Aah! Oh!

07:43.380 --> 07:45.047
l'm coming, buddy!

07:45.131 --> 07:46.674
[ punches landing ]

07:46.758 --> 07:49.843
All right, Invisibo,
eat a piece of this!

07:49.928 --> 07:51.512
[ grunts ]
Hurry, Finn!

07:51.596 --> 07:52.680
Get to the lever!

07:52.764 --> 07:53.973
Okay.

07:54.057 --> 07:54.890
Aah!

07:54.975 --> 07:55.849
l'm doing it!

08:00.605 --> 08:01.563
Aw, yeah!

08:01.648 --> 08:03.983
The imaginary poison is gone, Jake!

08:04.067 --> 08:05.359
Jake?

08:05.443 --> 08:06.527
[ moans ]

08:06.611 --> 08:07.861
Hey, come on.

08:07.946 --> 08:09.071
Wake up, man.

08:09.155 --> 08:10.823
Hello, Finn.

08:10.907 --> 08:12.241
l am awake and healthy.

08:12.325 --> 08:15.786
Jake, what happened to your
bombastic personality?

08:15.870 --> 08:18.122
l do not know what you mean.

08:18.206 --> 08:19.623
l am perfectly bombastic.

08:19.708 --> 08:21.000
Nah, man, nah.

08:21.084 --> 08:22.126
Something's wrong.

08:22.210 --> 08:23.669
Tell me something amazing.

08:23.753 --> 08:26.797
But, Finn, I cannot tell
you something amazing as

08:26.881 --> 08:29.591
there is nothing amazing
happening around us that l can

08:29.676 --> 08:30.551
describe for you.

08:30.635 --> 08:31.635
Aw, see, man?

08:31.720 --> 08:32.553
You suck now!

08:32.636 --> 08:34.054
Crap.
lt's your imagination.

08:34.139 --> 08:35.222
You need that thing.

08:35.306 --> 08:37.390
[ sighs ]

08:37.475 --> 08:38.308
[ violin drones ]

08:40.477 --> 08:41.520
Jake, stop it, man.

08:41.604 --> 08:43.813
You're just playing one
continuous note.

08:43.898 --> 08:46.025
One note is all
that is needed.

08:46.109 --> 08:47.026
[ scoffs ]

08:47.110 --> 08:49.862
l'm gonna turn your
imagination back on.

08:49.946 --> 08:51.739
Uh...where...

08:51.823 --> 08:54.575
Jake, your imagination on/off
switch has vanished!

08:54.659 --> 08:55.451
True.

08:55.535 --> 08:58.495
Doth thou not remember
shutting down mine imagination?

08:58.580 --> 08:59.872
l remembereth.

08:59.956 --> 09:03.208
l am happy that my
imagination is gone.

09:03.293 --> 09:04.293
lt was purposeless.

09:04.377 --> 09:06.879
No, it was the opposite
of that stuff.

09:06.963 --> 09:10.049
l know this now,
only too late.

09:10.133 --> 09:13.302
Okay, man, l'm gonna try to
imagine an imagination-back-on

09:13.386 --> 09:14.303
switch for you.

09:14.387 --> 09:15.888
And so you know, if there's

09:15.972 --> 09:17.306
anything dainty inside my imagination,

09:17.390 --> 09:19.183
l'm gonna be...

09:19.267 --> 09:20.476
Mad!

09:20.560 --> 09:23.145
lmagination go!

09:24.564 --> 09:26.440
What the stuff?

09:26.524 --> 09:27.524
Well...

09:27.609 --> 09:29.359
This isn't so bad.

09:29.444 --> 09:30.527
Nothing lame, at least.

09:30.612 --> 09:33.447
Hey, and there's Jake's
imagination switch!

09:33.531 --> 09:36.992
♪ Welcome to your
lmagination Land ♪

09:37.077 --> 09:39.369
♪ l am your
imagination band ♪

09:39.454 --> 09:40.954
Cram!

09:41.039 --> 09:43.499
Oh, maybe l can try
imagining something.

09:43.583 --> 09:45.626
Hmm!

09:45.710 --> 09:48.587
♪ lmagination cans ♪

09:48.671 --> 09:50.756
♪ We can shake our
imagination cans ♪

09:50.840 --> 09:51.632
Oh!

09:51.716 --> 09:52.674
[ laughs ]

09:52.759 --> 09:53.759
Now for that switch.

09:53.843 --> 09:55.803
[ British accent ]
Good morrow, Sir.

09:55.887 --> 09:57.304
My name is Bellamy Bug.

09:57.388 --> 10:00.766
Would you care for a crocheted
doily my daughter made?

10:00.850 --> 10:02.476
She imbued it with her tears.

10:02.560 --> 10:04.228
You see, she recently broke up

10:04.312 --> 10:05.521
with a gentle dandy.

10:05.605 --> 10:06.396
No!

10:06.481 --> 10:08.941
How'd youget in
my lmagination Land?!

10:09.025 --> 10:10.109
[ laughs ]

10:10.193 --> 10:12.277
l don't know,
my young fellow.

10:12.362 --> 10:13.529
Youtell me.

10:13.613 --> 10:17.407
Perhaps I represent your secret
desire to be civilized.

10:17.492 --> 10:18.951
Represent this!

10:19.035 --> 10:20.619
[ grunts ]
And this!

10:20.703 --> 10:21.745
[ grunting ]

10:21.830 --> 10:24.373
Oh, l say! Oh! Oh!

10:24.457 --> 10:27.376
Ow! Ouch! Oh! Ow!

10:27.460 --> 10:28.293
[ penguins wenking ]

10:28.378 --> 10:29.211
[ chuckles ]

10:29.295 --> 10:31.338
Penguins.
[ laughs ]

10:31.422 --> 10:32.756
All right.

10:32.841 --> 10:35.259
l hope this works, Jake.

10:35.343 --> 10:36.135
[ gasps ]

10:36.219 --> 10:37.302
[ laughs ]
Yeah!

10:37.387 --> 10:38.220
[ fairy giggles ]

10:38.304 --> 10:39.596
Huh?
Hey, get away from that.

10:39.681 --> 10:42.141
Don't push that
"Hyper Drive" button.

10:42.225 --> 10:43.892
Aaaaaaaaaaaaaah!

10:43.977 --> 10:46.478
l can imagine everything!

10:46.563 --> 10:47.896
[ grunts ]

10:47.981 --> 10:49.273
Take a hike, Fairy!

10:49.357 --> 10:50.440
Normal style!

10:50.525 --> 10:51.400
Aah!

10:51.484 --> 10:52.276
Oh!

10:52.360 --> 10:53.360
Oh, man.

10:53.444 --> 10:56.280
l imagined my mom naked.
Yuck!

10:56.364 --> 10:57.865
Jake, you okay?

10:57.949 --> 10:59.283
l think so.

10:59.367 --> 11:00.409
Let me check.

11:00.493 --> 11:01.994
Mm. Mm.

11:02.078 --> 11:03.287
Yep, she's clothed now.

11:03.371 --> 11:05.330
And, hey, man,
it's clear out now!

11:05.415 --> 11:06.832
We can go on an adventure!

11:06.916 --> 11:08.333
l don't know, dude.

11:08.418 --> 11:12.296
l think we got all the adventure
we need right here with...

11:12.380 --> 11:13.297
Lava on the floor!

11:13.381 --> 11:14.173
Huh?!

11:14.257 --> 11:16.133
Aah! Aah!

11:16.217 --> 11:18.135
My legs are melting!

11:18.219 --> 11:19.219
Just kidding.

11:19.304 --> 11:20.345
[ both laugh ]

11:20.430 --> 11:21.471
Good dog.

11:23.433 --> 11:27.102
♪ Come along with me ♪

11:27.187 --> 11:31.106
